    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Solid good-condition car that presents well overall and should make a very usable, enjoyable driver. The exterior, interior, and overall finish show normal age-related wear consistent with a well-kept car that has been used and maintained, rather than stored as a showpiece. It still has a clean, attractive appearance and should appeal to someone looking for a nice honest example they can drive and enjoy without paying mint-condition money.",
