    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Fair, honest car that appears usable as-is but shows clear age and wear throughout. Expect visible cosmetic blemishes, interior wear, and the sort of imperfections and deferred-maintenance items common in an older driver. It still presents decently enough for someone looking for an affordable entry point, but buyers should come in expecting a car with flaws rather than a polished example.",
